                    <h2 class="main-title">Why we love Peckham</h2>
                    <div class="header_title_border" style="margin:0 auto;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-lg-12 para-justify">
                <p>No longer an undiscovered secret, Peckham has quickly become one of the most popular locations for prospective buyers and tenants &#x2013; and it isn&#x2019;t difficult to see why.</p>
                <p>Peckham Rye&#x2019;s cool credentials and small town vibe offers wonderful housing options, a wide array of independent boutiques and an excellent selection of pubs and popular restaurants ranging from street food to fine dining.</p>
                <p>Paired with its easy access to transport links into central London and the West End, Peckham offers the best of village and city life, appealing to residents of all ages.</p>
                <p>Think Peckham could be the place for you? Get in touch with our team to start your search.</p>
                <div class="mt-3">
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Talk to our team</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="intro" style="background:#fff; padding:40px 0;">
